<br>
<i>Dear Athelfi,<br>
<br>
I have had a dire emergency that I must attend.  My daughter, Diana, some of you do know her...has been caught in another time and is gravely ill.  I must attend her as quick as possible and am sorry all I can do is leave you a note.  <br>
<br>
While I am gone...look to Tasha and DeLerium as they have our Rite of Caste.  Also turn to your athelfi and other Queen's.  I will return before you know it.  And shall constantly be thinking about you all.<br>
<br>
Hippolyte </i><br>
